title: File:Taman Mini Indonesia Indah Archipelago Lake Viewing Tower.jpg
author: RasyaAbhirama13
description: The viewing tower (left of the photo) at the west side of the archipelago lake of Taman Mini Indonesia Indah, East Jakarta, Jakarta, Indonesia. It is one of the new attractions in TMII which was built during the revitalization of TMII in 2022.
